    waitForEventComplete: 0
    waitDuration: 2
  - isExpanded: 0
    stepName: Wait 1 sec
    stepType: 2
    textLines:
    - <color=#D4AF37>Sleeping on the job?
    - <color=white>What?
    - <color=#D4AF37>How is the SS Cadence going to navigate the waters without you?
    - <color=white>It's not here yet.
    - I need rest to perform.
    - <color=#D4AF37>Is the sonar monitor still giving you problems?
    - <color=white>No.
    - <color=#D4AF37>How did you fix it?
    - <color=white>The circuit board was corroded.
    - The last crate of supplies had some alcohol.
    - <color=#D4AF37>What about the pipe organ?
    - <color=#D4AF37>You haven't performed in a while.
    - <color=white>It's fine.
    - <color=#D4AF37>And you?
    - <color=white>Hungry. Exhausted.
    - <color=#D4AF37>Are you completely out of supplies?
    - <color=white>I'll help the SS Cadence navigate through the rocks and they'll
      drop supplies for me.
    - The ships always do.
    - <color=#D4AF37>You had a rough time with the last ship.
    - <color=#D4AF37>It hit quite a few rocks.
    - <color=white>But they made it through.
    - <color=#D4AF37>Yes.
    - <color=white>And I got my supplies.
    - <color=#D4AF37>Barely.
    - <color=white>Well the monitor is fixed now, so...
    - <color=#D4AF37>Elara.
    - <color=white>Yeah?
    - <color=#D4AF37>They're here.
